    "Field workAccording to the literature, the most advanced methods for preventing legal problems focus on contract risk management [43].",
    "So, we ground our research on effectivity of contract automation and iContracts [7,26].",
    "iContracts are based on the hybrid approach between human and computer interventions that aim to achieve full automation with self-executing contracts [102].",
    "Owing to their compliance with Hybrid AI principles, contract automation enables state-of-the-art innovations [103].While investigating contract automation, we observed that two main processes are not given sufficient attention, viz.",
    "(1) the communication process preceding the drafting of contracts and (2) the risk analysis during the drafting of contracts [26]."
